下點, <br />\n呢幾晚用電腦成日都彈出嚟要我reboot煩到死"},{"pid":"308e9d4a986ef3b5be3075e9246364ec459d5b4f","tid":229840,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解 windows update 要 disable 防毒 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網見到好多人都話防毒有機會令到有啲嘢裝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好多人話update時熄咗佢又得, 咪試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申乜都唔識</blockquote><br />\nwindows update 要 disable 防毒先裝到<br />\n咁係呢個 windows update 有毒<br />\n定呢個防毒誤報 ?"},{"pid":"8bfa2d8ba1f4812662bbc4e198f9e1e625c697cb","tid":229840,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"試下clean完屎眼再升啦<br />\n我clean 完屎眼之後升級ok"},{"pid":"222bd242c1b6f1896ae16a5ab92705c9afd73282","tid":229840,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下clean完屎眼再升啦<br />\n我clean 完屎眼之後升級ok</blockquote><br />\n屎眼係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a591b2d7238cee06463d385cd229c3d97468c48","tid":229840,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"我半年更新唔到<br />\n留名學野"},{"pid":"5c7441ca5b730ab91a6a25b8743ed174e1c02477","tid":229840,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有hardware同windows 10 1703 撞咗<br />\n升唔到<br />\n再等多一排睇MS點搞啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/microsoft-warns-not-to-install-windows-10-creators-update-manually/software/win10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2Fmicrosoft-warns-not-to-install-windows-10-creators-update-manually%2Fsoftware%2Fwin10%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=bddcb365\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/microsoft-warns-not-to-install-windows-10-creators-update-manually/software/win10/</a></blockquote><br />\nLinux 啲 packages 好似唔會有 conflicts <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次聽過 windows update 會同 hardware 有衝突</blockquote><br />\n應該係講 driver <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手快快無講清楚<br />\n外國發現有d case係hardware driver會有問題<br />\n如上面link嘅bluetooth connection呢d小問題<br />\n有d 問題係一裝更新就入唔到去windows<br />\n仲有d 舊嘅CPU LOAD更新會出彈不支援windows 10 creator<br />\n(呢個應該未解決到) <br />\n<br />\n唔知樓主咩原因<br />\n如果唔急用d 功能唔使理佢<br />\n急用就試下format部機，clean晒先裝<br />\n見到有d人係咁就無啦啦解決咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c36929d14be1766168000cb658b19a7f336d96","tid":229840,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我半年更新唔到<br />\n留名學野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你彈咩問題先？"},{"pid":"3983eae47586e815ad2347c27704066a4646963f","tid":229840,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下clean完屎眼再升啦<br />\n我clean 完屎眼之後升級ok</blockquote><br />\n屎眼係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係windows 10成日痾屎，你又唔記得幫佢抹屎眼，咁個屎眼太污糟塞住左，windows 10就可能痾唔出屎囉"},{"pid":"ebca2bbd8e7002b8ae653690eecb019b6266ea9b","tid":229840,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我半年更新唔到<br />\n留名學野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你彈咩問題先？</blockquote><br />\n0x80080005<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85d8f7bdb2623d5c3c8a8e5bbf79bee99e33f5e","tid":229840,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite